<template>
  <Connexion status="login"/>
</template>

<script>
import Connexion from '@/components/connection/Connexion'
export default {
    name:'Login',
    components:{
        Connexion
    },
    mounted(){
        this.verificationLogin()
    },
    methods:{
        verificationLogin(){
        if (!this.$store.getters.getLogged)
          this.$router.push('/home')
      }
    }
}
</script>
